title: Flu (Optional)
body: Researchers are studying the effectiveness of a particular flu vaccine. A large random sample was taken from the population of people who took the vaccine in $$2016$$. Among the sampled people, 48% did not get the flu. Another large random sample was taken in $$2017$$, from among the people who took the vaccine that year. Among these sampled people, 40% did not get the flu.
